
basic typography
-------------------
classes
-------

lead -- to change default style of paragraphs.
font-weight-bold
font-ialic

text-lowercase
text-capitalize

blockquote
blockquote-footer

text-truncate -- to change to single line paragraphs

list items
-------------
list-unstyled - ul
list-inline - ul
    list-inline-item -li 



Text ALignment And Display
--------------------------
class = 'text-justify'

text-center


tetxt-right

 <!-- ALIGNMENT -->
    <p class="text-left">Text aligned left</p>
    <p class="text-center">Text aligned center</p>
    <p class="text-right">Text aligned right</p>


inline , block and inline-block
--------------------------------
d-inline
d-block
d-inline-block


bg
--------------
bg-success -green
bg-danger -red
bg-dark -dark
bg-light - light


clearfix
---------------
class="clearfix"

to clear float, so so elements
comes after it will be under the floated elements .


position
--------

classes
-------------------------------------------
fixed-top -- element fixed at top always we scroll
sticky-top  -- element start to stick to top when reach the element by scroll
fixed-bottom

COLORS AND BaCKGROUNDS
------------------------


 <!-- TEXT COLORS -->
        <p class="text-primary">Text Primary Color</p>
        <p class="text-secondary">Text Secondary Color</p>
        <p class="text-success">Text Success Color</p>
        <p class="text-info">Text Info Color</p>
        <p class="text-warning">Text Warning Color</p>
        <p class="text-danger">Text Danger Color</p>
        <p class="text-light">Text Light Color</p>
        <p class="text-dark">Text Dark Color</p>
        <p class="text-white">Text White Color</p>
        <p class="text-muted" >Text Muted</p>
        <p class="text-black-50">Text Black 50</p>
        <p class="text-white-50">Text White 50</p>

        <br>
        <br>

